6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating agriculture; repealing 2 O.S. 2021,
Sections 2-18, as amended by Section 608, Chapter
8 486, O.S.L. 2025, 2A-28, and 20-8 (2 O.S. Supp. 2025,
Section 2-18), which relate to the Department of
9 Agriculture Food and Forestry administrative law
judges; and providing an effective date.
